&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://YLine-hub.github.io/p/vmware%E7%9A%84centos%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85vmwaretools/image-8.png&#34;
	width=&#34;586&#34;
